``bytes index-of``
[link: /commands/categories/bytes.md] ’Щ@c269c9aa300292b5a950442b89ee2383a4fda14f6ed72351c77ac9f70da1083eЩeTitle: title: bytes index-of
Path: Signature
Content:
``> bytes index-of {flags} (pattern) ...rest``
’Щ@5a23f27b157a378aac13e69f5915484eccb97b5d0c75f8e988503c11585841ecЩҗTitle: title: bytes index-of
Path: Flags
Content:
``--all, -a``
: Returns all matched index.
``--end, -e``
: Search from the end of the binary.
’Щ@d843ea5bf34fb8f322da603e7255f59c6346491d9b948e6189d3db6341c016dbЩ·Title: title: bytes index-of
Path: Parameters
Content:
``pattern``
: The pattern to find index of.
``...rest``
: For a data structure input, find the indexes at the given cell paths.
